de.filters.help:
Selecting multiple elements of the lists grouped together
  1. Click the first element you want to select, and then press and hold the Shift key.
  2. While holding Shift, click the last item you want to select.
Select multiple elements that are not grouped together
  1. Click the first element you want to select, and then press and hold the Ctrl key.
  2. While holding down the Ctrl key, click each of the other items you want to select.
